question: Which café can I find towards Scarsdale American Legion Post 52 Memorial Garden, Scarsdale, NY within 80 kilometers from the Juilliard School, New York, NY?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.983102 40.773839)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.762298 40.979409)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'cafe'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.983102 40.773839)',4326)::geography, 80000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-73.983102 40.773839)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
